No tricks, here... Get festive with these Spooky Spider Cupcakes and Marshmallow Mummy Cupcakes this Halloween.

<strong>Items Needed for Spooky Spider Cupcakes: </strong>Cupcakes (Order Ukrop's cupcakes from <a href="http://bit.ly/DecoratedCakes" target="_blank">bit.ly/DecoratedCakes</a>), black icing, York Peppermint Patties and Mini M&amp;Ms.

Step 1: We started with a Ukrop's Cupcake.

<img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1859" alt="CupcakeStep1" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4836-300x200.jpg" width="300" height="200" />

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

Step 2: Place York Peppermint Patty on Cupcake.

<img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1860" alt="CupcakeStep2" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4837-300x200.jpg" width="300" height="200" />

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

Step 3: Draw spider legs on cupcake with icing. We drew six legs.

<img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1861" alt="CupcakeStep3" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4847-300x200.jpg" width="300" height="200" />

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1880" alt="SpiderLegs" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4852-300x200.jpg" width="300" height="200" />

Step 4: Now the eyes. Put a small dab of icing on one Mini M&amp;M and place it on the York Peppermint Patty. Repeat for the second eye.

<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1865" alt="CupcakeStep4" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4861-300x200.jpg" width="300" height="200" />

And, voila! You have your Spooky Spider Cupcake... Great for whole family to make and enjoy together.

<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1869" alt="CupcakeFinishedProduct" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4866-300x200.jpg" width="300" height="200" />

<strong>Items Needed for Marshmallow Mummy Cupcakes: </strong>Cupcakes (Order Ukrop's cupcakes from <a href="http://bit.ly/DecoratedCakes" target="_blank">bit.ly/DecoratedCakes</a>), Marshmallows, Mini M&amp;Ms, and a tool for cutting the marshmallows.

Step 1: We began by cutting two lines into the cupcakes.

<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1873" alt="CuttingMarshmallow" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4794-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" />

Step 2: Pick any color M&amp;M and place it into the marshmallow for an eye. We chose blue for one cupcake and green for another.

<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1874" alt="PlaceMandM" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4797-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" />

Step 3: Repeat for the second eye.

<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1875" alt="Place2ndMandM" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4802-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" />

Step 4: Place a final M&amp;M in the marshmallow for the mouth.

<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1876" alt="PlaceMandMMouth" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4805-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" />

Step 5: Carefully place the marshmallow onto the cupcake.

<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1877" alt="PlaceontoCupcake" src="http://ukropshomestylefoods.com/site/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/IMG_4810-200x300.jpg" width="200" height="300" />

That's it! And now you have sweet treats for Halloween.

